OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry this
OL,6,Fevening with some clear spells but
OL,7,Fturning cloudier overnight with a
OL,8,Fscattering of showers by dawn, these
OL,9,Fmainly focused in the west. Chilly in
OL,10,Fplaces underneath the clearest skies.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA mixed picture with
OL,13,Foccasional bright or sunny spells
OL,14,Fthrough the day and further showers.
OL,15,FFeeling slightly warmer than Wednesday
OL,16,Fwith light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
