OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:
OL,6,FChangeable with showers on Friday,
OL,7,Fturning locally heavy at times and
OL,8,Fdeveloping into more widespread and
OL,9,Fpersistent rain on Saturday. Drier on
OL,10,FSunday. Turning warmer briefly.
